# Detection 13: Failed Logins by Location
# MITRE ATT&CK: T1110 (Brute Force)
# Description: Geographic sources of failed login attempts to identify attack origins
# Severity: Medium

index=azure_logs
| spath status.errorCode
| spath location.city
| spath location.countryOrRegion
| where 'status.errorCode' != 0
| stats count as FailedAttempts by location.city, location.countryOrRegion
| sort - FailedAttempts
